name: CRYPTO NEVER SLEEPS... BUT I SHOULD...

metadata.name: CRYPTO NEVER SLEEPS… BUT I SHOULD… #2
metadata.description:
‘CRYPTO NEVER SLEEPS… BUT I SHOULD…’ marks the official launch of the NFSHE brand. The project aims to promote balance among the crypto community. After all, even though crypto never sleeps, we all should.



Perks & Utility:

SLEEP MASK

Receive a physical ‘CRYPTO NEVER SLEEPS… BUT I SHOULD…’ sleep mask


EVENT ACCESS

Functions as a ticket to one NFSHEvent


RARITY

Each ‘CRYPTO NEVER SLEEPS… BUT I SHOULD…’ NFSHE is numbered


NFSHE HOLDER COMMUNITY

Be one of the first members of the NFSHE Holder Community



Policy:

All sales are final. Only primary sales are eligible for a physical item and one redeemable NFSHEvent ticket
